videos.headline: Wilson makes remarkable leaping grab for Ohio State
videos.description: Garrett Wilson climbs the ladder to make an incredible catch that is originally ruled incomplete, but is later overturned to put Ohio State in the red zone.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Wilson makes remarkable leaping grab for Ohio State) 2019/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dobbins turns on burners for long TD run
videos.description: J.K. Dobbins breaks free for a 68-yard touchdown run for the Buckeyes to increase their first-quarter lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Dobbins turns on burners for long TD run) 2019/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Higgins' helmet jars loose on incomplete pass, exits game
videos.description: Tee Higgins exits the game after hitting the ground and losing his helmet on an incomplete pass from Trevor Lawrence.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Higgins' helmet jars loose on incomplete pass, exits game) 2019/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dobbins breaks free again for huge gain
videos.description: J.K. Dobbins breaks off his second run of 60-plus yards to plant the Buckeyes inside Clemson territory.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Dobbins breaks free again for huge gain) 2019/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dobbins drops potential TD from Fields
videos.description: J.K. Dobbins cannot complete the process of a touchdown catch as the original call on the field is reversed to an incomplete pass.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Dobbins drops potential TD from Fields) 2019/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lawrence shaken up after big hit, Wade ejected for targeting
videos.description: Shaun Wade is ejected for targeting after hitting Trevor Lawrence above the shoulders.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Lawrence shaken up after big hit, Wade ejected for targeting) 2019/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Etienne maneuvers around the defense into the end zone
videos.description: Travis Etienne takes the pitch and avoids multiple tackles while getting into the end zone for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Etienne maneuvers around the defense into the end zone) 2019/12/28

videos.headline: Lawrence snaps ankles en route to 67-yard TD
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence puts an Ohio State defender on the ground with a juke and then busts loose for a 67-yard Clemson touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Lawrence snaps ankles en route to 67-yard TD) 2019/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ohio State, Clemson go back and forth in first half
videos.description: After Ohio State gets out to a 16-0 lead, Clemson comes back with two touchdowns by Etienne and Lawrence to cut the Buckeyes' lead to two at halftime.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Ohio State, Clemson go back and forth in first half) 2019/12/28 SOTFULL

videos.headline: Dobbins walks gingerly to locker room after reaggravating ankle
videos.description: J.K. Dobbins heads to the locker room after reinjuring his ankle on a non-contact play.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Dobbins walks gingerly to locker room after reaggravating ankle) 2019/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Etienne bolts to the house on TD from Lawrence
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence flips a pass to Travis Etienne, who finds a seam and motors to the end zone for a 53-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Etienne bolts to the house on TD from Lawrence) 2019/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Simmons swoops over to intercept Fields
videos.description: Justin Fields' interception to Isaiah Simmons in the third quarter marks the first turnover of the PlayStation Fiesta Bowl.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Simmons swoops over to intercept Fields) 2019/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ohio State's fumble TD overturned after review
videos.description: Ohio State thought they got a fumble recovery for a touchdown; but after review, it was ruled the ball was incomplete.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ohio State's fumble TD overturned after review) 2019/12/28

videos.headline: Buckeyes reclaim lead on Fields' 4th-down TD strike
videos.description: Ohio State rolls the dice on 4th-and-2, as Justin Fields fires a 23-yard touchdown to Chris Olave to regain the lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Buckeyes reclaim lead on Fields' 4th-down TD strike) 2019/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lawrence sells fake, fires jump pass for go-ahead TD
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence gets the Ohio State defense to bite on a pump fake, then whips a pass to Travis Etienne for a 34-yard Clemson touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Lawrence sells fake, fires jump pass for go-ahead TD) 2019/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Turner picks off Fields to seal Clemson's trip to title game
videos.description: Justin Fields is picked off in the end zone by Nolan Turner, sealing a trip to the CFP title game for Clemson.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Turner picks off Fields to seal Clemson's trip to title game) 2019/12/29

videos.headline: Swinney: 'This is how a championship game oughta be!'
videos.description: Dabo Swinney reflects on the final moments of Clemson's PlayStation Fiesta Bowl victory over Ohio State, including Nolan Turner's game-winning interception.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Swinney: 'This is how a championship game oughta be!') 2019/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lawrence: 'I really love this team'
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence in disbelief about the comeback win and shows his appreciation for his teammates.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Lawrence: 'I really love this team') 2019/12/28

videos.headline: Day 'angry' over Ohio State's missed opportunities
videos.description: Ryan Day expresses his disappointment over Ohio State's loss to Clemson in the PlayStation Fiesta Bowl, admitting chances were missed at key points in the game.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Day 'angry' over Ohio State's missed opportunities) 2019/12/28

videos.headline: Clemson shows championship mettle on game-winning drive
videos.description: Trailing by two with less than three minutes to play, Clemson drives 94 yards in four plays to score the game-winning touchdown against Ohio State.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Clemson shows championship mettle on game-winning drive) 2019/12/28 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Swinney: Clemson showed the heart of a champion vs. Ohio State
videos.description: Dabo Swinney commends the Buckeyes' toughness throughout the Fiesta Bowl, but says his Tigers showed the "heart of a champion" in their wire-to-wire victory.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Swinney: Clemson showed the heart of a champion vs. Ohio State) 2019/12/28 ESHEET SVP
